    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《鬼子必须死》是一款融合FPS搜打撤+根据地生存建造的抗战游戏，玩家将扮演游击队员深入敌后，消灭鬼子，夺取物资，并将物资用于根据地建设。通过根据地种田+建造让队伍活下去，最终光复县城。（支持单人游戏和最多4人联机）</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家讨论群：697960286，780667330</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游击队的搜打撤</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演游击队，袭击鬼子的运输队，获取各种物资并且成功从鬼子围剿中撤退。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309070/extras/b16026af7a16efa093da32a23c4c4693.poster.avif?t=1770891652\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309070/extras/b16026af7a16efa093da32a23c4c4693.webm?t=1770891652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309070/extras/b16026af7a16efa093da32a23c4c4693.mp4?t=1770891652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样化的武器系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包括抗战大刀，驳壳枪，中正式等经典武器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309070/extras/4e61023c7f77c19dc45abbd6e026aef1.poster.avif?t=1770891652\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309070/extras/4e61023c7f77c19dc45abbd6e026aef1.webm?t=1770891652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309070/extras/4e61023c7f77c19dc45abbd6e026aef1.mp4?t=1770891652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还可以通过黑市商人和图纸仿制来获得各种同时代的欧美武器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有武器都可以去根据地升级，例如驳壳枪可以安装快慢机变成全自动模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309070/extras/3fe3c4c37d85244db8561b69c0eae553.poster.avif?t=1770891652\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309070/extras/3fe3c4c37d85244db8561b69c0eae553.webm?t=1770891652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309070/extras/3fe3c4c37d85244db8561b69c0eae553.mp4?t=1770891652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >根据地建设和种田</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自己动手丰衣足食，可以通过建设根据地和种田来获取食物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以通过饲养牲畜来获得肉食，并且牲畜的粪便可以制作肥料提升耕地质量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >食物可以制作食品回复生命并且提升各项属性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据地可以开矿冶炼，利用获得的武器图纸来生产和升级武器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309070/extras/ba3b5e46463b6806860538330b40f785.poster.avif?t=1770891652\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309070/extras/ba3b5e46463b6806860538330b40f785.webm?t=1770891652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309070/extras/ba3b5e46463b6806860538330b40f785.mp4?t=1770891652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
